'''Keith Barker''' (born February 11, 1959) is a sailor who competed for the [[British Virgin Islands]].

Barker with his older brother [[Peter Barker (sailor)|Peter Barker]] competed at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]] in [[Los Angeles]], they entered the [[Sailing at the 1984 Summer Olympics – 470|470 class]] and out of 28 crews they finished 25th.<ref>{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ba/keith-barker-1.html}}</ref>

