{{Infobox gymnast |name= Tzveta Kousseva |gender= w |image= |image_size= |caption= |fullname= |altname= |nickname= |country= {{flagu|Bulgaria}} |regions= |formercountry= |birth_date= {{birth date and age|1989|1|6|df=y}} |birth_place= |hometown= |residence= |death_date= |death_place= |height= |discipline= RG |level= Senior International Elite |natlteam= 2007-2008 (?) |club= |gym= |collegeteam= |headcoach= |assistcoach= |formercoach= |choreographer= |music= |eponymousskills= |retired= |worldranking= |updated= |show-medals= yes |medaltemplates= <!-- see [[Template:MedalRelatedTemplates]] --> }}
'''Tzveta Kousseva''' ({{lang-bg|Цвета Кусева}}) (born {{birth date|1989|1|6|df=yes}}) was a [[Bulgaria]]n group [[rhythmic gymnast]]. She represented her nation at international competitions.
She participated at the [[2008 Summer Olympics]] in Beijing.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20170312031215/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1A1-D92ND7204.html] </ref> She also competed at world championships, including at the [[2007 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships]].<ref>{{cite web|title=2007 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships athletes - Tzveta Kousseva|url=http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/000006030100FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF01|website=Longinestiming.com|date= |accessdate=27 January 2016}}</ref>
